item.content:encoded:
About us

We are an exciting new concept brand dedicated to delivering innovative 3D led lights.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LgCaDIGbXIc&ab_channel=StudioCheha

Were passionate about creative lighting design and glean inspiration for our original style from people's kindest memories and nostalgic experiences. Focusing always on taking a modern twist to our designs, our creative yet functional indoor lighting will be the focal point of any room.

Were committed to making a difference in our community, reducing our impact on the environment, and using high-tech LED lighting technology to power all of our energy-saving designs.

Our main goal is to provide the best service to our customers through what we do, offer and deliver and make them feel special with our perspective on how lights should be: unique.

About our product

 

Optical Visual Illusion through the acrylic board.
Friendly for kids, the acrylic panel is strong and hard, not fragile.
Soft brightness is not harmful to the eyes.
Safety and Energy-saving with low power.
Powered by USB cable.

About Us

The way we chose to stand out is that we don't want our customers to just inspire us, we want them to be part of our products' final result.

The concept of customizing your product opens the door to thousands of possibilities and options. We all want our products to be unique, but in this case, they really can be.

We want to offer the public, quality service, innovative products, and also the certainty that they can receive a product that no one has, simply because it's based on their ideas.

item.title: Blog
item.dc:creator: Mujo2023
item.content:encoded:
Blog

Its time to get your owl decoration

We always hear its important when the exterior matches the interior, especially if its for good. While colors can provide a positive psychological impact on humans, lamps and lighting, on the other side, can visually impact our favourite indoor places wherever we are. But not everyone realizes that lighting fixtures, particularly table lamps, are becoming an essential part of every interior. They can create a mood, change an atmosphere and even play roles as important as any other furnishing.

If we can see beyond the light provided, its possible to face table lamps as tools that can define functional zones within a room and accentuate the emotional impact of specific spaces. The right choice of a quality product or being able to customize your own with a nostalgic or emotionally appealing theme will pay off, by bringing you every day joyful experiences in your home.

The main criteria for successful lighting in todays homes are mobility and variety that could be easily implemented with quality. Choosing the right table lamp is a very personal business. You should start by defining for yourself what kind of mood you are trying to achieve within your home or in a particular room. After all, table lamps are a very easy way of self-expression, thanks to the possibility of customizing them.

They can fit into bedrooms, for adults or kids, on top of bedside tables, dressers, and shelves. Can be a good addition to your office, on the desks or shelves, but be careful, in professional environments its important to match the overall visual. And if youre looking for a cozy living room, these lamps are the perfect detail for your coffee table or illuminate your favourite place to read that book you just bought.

Remember always to choose a lamp that you can connect with. The size, style, and color of the light are important choices to consider, but at the end of the day being able to customize your lamp, brings you the possibility to have a product just like you: unique.

TAGS: table lamps, customized, decoration, office, bedroom, living room.

This lamp is made from laser-engraved acrylic and is designed to stay cool to the touch. The 3D shape is mirrored to have the illusion aspect on both sides. Its perfect for lounge mood lighting or comforting bedroom lighting. This product is available with all the color lights from our portfolio. Want a different theme or image? Thats no problem! Tell us your idea and we can customize the lamp just for you. Send us your reference images on our contact page.

item.title: 3D Geometric Table Lamp
item.dc:creator: Mujo2023
item.excerpt:encoded: Geometry with a new look is what defines our 3D Geometric Led Lamp. This shape lamp with geometric lines is an alternative and trendy option to meet a different and innovative style. This lamp is made from laser-engraved acrylic and is designed to stay cool to the touch. The 3D shape is mirrored to keep the aspect and view on both sides. Its perfect for lounge mood lighting or futuristic and modern living room lighting. This product is available with all the color lights from our portfolio. Want a different theme or image? Thats no problem! Tell us your idea and we can customize the lamp just for you. Send us your reference images on our contact page.

item.title: Personalized Text Table Lamp
item.dc:creator: Mujo2023
item.excerpt:encoded: Can you imagine having a cool lamp with your own name? Its possible. This 3D Led Lamp can have your name on it through personalized texts making it unique. This lamp is made from laser-engraved acrylic and is designed to stay cool to the touch. The name can be customized with a drawing style to the lamp. Its the perfect gift for friends, family and everyone you like. This product is available with all the color lights from our portfolio and you can choose from 5 different fonts to the name. Want a different theme or image? Thats no problem! Tell us your idea and we can customize the lamp just for you. Send us your reference images on our contact page.

item.title: Blog
item.dc:creator: Mujo2023
item.content:encoded:
Its time to get your owl decoration

We always hear its important when the exterior matches the interior, especially if its for good. While colors can provide a positive psychological impact on humans, lamps and lighting, on the other side, can visually impact our favourite indoor places wherever we are. But not everyone realizes that lighting fixtures, particularly table lamps, are becoming an essential part of every interior. They can create a mood, change an atmosphere and even play roles as important as any other furnishing. If we can see beyond the light provided, its possible to face table lamps as tools that can define functional zones within a room and accentuate the emotional impact of specific spaces. The right choice of a quality product or being able to customize your own with a nostalgic or emotionally appealing theme will pay off, by bringing you everyday joyful experiences in your home. The main criteria for successful lighting in todays homes are mobility and variety that could be easily implemented with quality. Choosing the right table lamp is a very personal business. You should start by defining for yourself what kind of mood you are trying to achieve within your home or in a particular room. After all, table lamps are a very easy way of self-expression, thanks to the possibility of customizing them. They can fit into bedrooms, for adults or kids, on top of bedside tables, dressers, and shelves. Can be a good addition to your office, on the desks or shelves, but be careful, in professional environments its important to match the overall visual. And if youre looking for a cozy living room, these lamps are the perfect detail for your coffee table or illuminate your favourite place to read that book you just bought. Remember always to choose a lamp that you can connect with. The size, style, and color of the light are important choices to consider, but at the end of the day being able to customize your lamp, brings you the possibility to have a product just like you: unique. TAGS: #table lamps, #customized, #decoration, #office, #bedroom, #living room.

item.title: What color are you?
item.dc:creator: Mujo2023
item.content:encoded:
Have you ever wondered how colored lights can directly impact you? Even in a psychological way? In a world of rush with busy routines, and schedules, it's difficult to pay attention to details or do one thing even further: look beyond them. And these details can be everywhere: clothes, food, friends, house, or how we decorate them specifically.

A "not that old" survey with lighting professionals has shown that color is a critical consideration in all lighting applications and it is typically more important than light efficacy. Artificial lighting can transform a space, but choosing the right color can make it stand out. They can enhance performances, worship productions, or just make a place more functional. And why is that? Because it has been proved that lighting and color variations have a psychological effect on humans.

We are surrounded by different types of light everywhere, they can be natural light which provides benefits for our health, fixed lights such as the main lights in our house, work, and school that can indirectly impact our behavior, and finally, we can have artificial lights such as led lamps with different colors that can impact our emotions.

Color in lighting can be transformative. Each color of light has a wavelength that affects our psychology and physiology. In many ways, proper lighting can offer individuals several benefits: blue or cooler-colored light has been shown to increase alertness and reduce eye strain. Warm and middle-colored light tones, like yellow, are also used to create inviting, intimate or relaxing spaces. Red light, in addition, has been shown to improve memory and attention to detail.

It's important to say that when it comes to these color interpretations, there is no right answer. And that is because, although our personalities don't change often, our emotions are constantly changing. They can be affected by people around us, situations we go through, memories, nostalgic feelings, and unexpected events, and these emotions can be related to certain colors. And that's exactly how the right color can be the right fit for who you are at that moment.

item.title: Owl lamp
item.dc:creator: Mujo2023
item.content:encoded: The perfect light for decorating almost any room. It has an acrylic glass sheet (laser engraved) that creates a stunning 3D effect. This 3d illusion LED lighting lasts up to 50,000 hours and stays cool to the touch, making it safe for children's rooms.
